<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.5.0/font/bootstrap-icons.css" />
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous" />
    <title>Hanz Airline</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f5e2d2;

        }

        :root {
            --theme-gradient: linear-gradient(45deg, #e67818, #800080);
            --theme-color: #ff69b4;
        }

        nav {
            background: var(--theme-gradient);
            color: black;
        }

        .content {
            margin-top: 70px;
            background-image: url("/assets/travel_info/bag8.jpg");
            background-size: cover;
            height: 650px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .section2 {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            flex-wrap: nowrap;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .responsive1 {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;

        }

        .cardSection {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            gap: 300px;
            margin: 20px 50px;
        }

        .bottom {
            margin-top: 70px;
            background-image: url("/assets/travel_info//img4.jpg");
            background-size: cover;
            height: 650px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <%- include("./partials/nav") %>

        <div class="content">
            <div class="section pb-5">
                <h1>When traveling with us, <br /></h1>
                <h4>
                    we ensure that your baggage needs are well taken care of. <br />Please
                    review the information below to understand our baggage policies.
                </h4>
            </div>
        </div>
        <section id="baggage-allowance">
            <br><br>

            <h1 class="text-center m-4">Baggage Allowance</h1>

            <div class="section2">
                <div class="responsive">
                    <div class="gallery">
                        <img src="/assets/travel_info/bag1.jpg" alt="BagImg1" width="600" height="400">
                        </a>
                        <!--div class="desc">Add a description of the image here</div>-->
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="responsive">
                    <div class="gallery">
                        <img src="/assets/travel_info/bag2.jpg" alt="BagImg2" width="600" height="400">
                        </a>
                        <!--div class="desc">Add a description of the image here</div>-->
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="responsive1 center">
                <div class="gallery">
                    <img src="/assets/travel_info/bag9.jpg" class="img-fluid" alt="BagImg3" width="600" height="400">
                    </a>
                    <!--div class="desc">Add a description of the image here</div>-->
                </div>
            </div>

            <h5>
                <p>Each passenger is allowed to carry a certain amount of baggage without incurring additional charges.
                    The standard allowance is as follows:</p>
                <h6>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Economy Class: 1 checked bag (up to 23 kg) and 1 carry-on bag (up to 7 kg)</li>
                        <li>Business Class: 2 checked bags (up to 32 kg each) and 2 carry-on bags (up to 7 kg each)</li>
                        <li>First Class: 3 checked bags (up to 32 kg each) and 2 carry-on bags (up to 7 kg each)</li>
                        <br>
                        <p>Please note: Excess baggage may incur additional fees.</p>
                    </ul>
                </h6>
            </h5>
        </section>
        <section id="additional-baggage">

            <br><br>


            <h1 class="text-center m-4">Additional Baggage</h1>
            <div class="responsive1 center">
                <div class="gallery">
                    <img src="/assets/travel_info/bag10.jpg" class="img-fluid" alt="BagImg4" width="600" height="400">
                    </a>
                    <!--div class="desc">Add a description of the image here</div>-->
                </div>
            </div>
            <h5>
                <p>If you need to bring more baggage than the standard allowance, you may purchase additional baggage
                    weight during booking or at the airport.</p>
            </h5>
            <h6>
                <ul>
                    <li>Additional checked baggage is subject to availability and additional charges.</li>
                    <li>The cost of excess baggage varies depending on your destination and class of service.</li>
                </ul>
            </h6>
        </section>

        <br><br>

        <h1 class="text-center m-4">General Information</h1>
        <div class="section2">
            <div class="responsive">
                <div class="gallery">
                    <img src="/assets/travel_info/img1.jpg" alt="Img1" width="600" height="400">
                    </a>
                    <!--div class="desc">Add a description of the image here</div>-->
                </div>
            </div><br>

            <div class="responsive">
                <div class="gallery">
                    <img src="/assets/travel_info/img2.jpg" alt="Img2" width="600" height="400">
                    </a>
                    <!--div class="desc">Add a description of the image here</div>-->
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <h5>
            <p>Before you travel, it's important to be aware of the following general information to ensure a smooth
                journey:</p>
        </h5>
        <h6>
            <ul>
                <li><b>Check-In:</b> Online check-in is available 24 hours before departure. You may also check in at
                    the airport counter.</li>
                <li><b>Security:</b> Liquids, gels, and aerosols in carry-on bags must be in containers of no more than
                    100 ml each and placed
                    in a single, transparent, resealable bag.</li>
                <li><b>Flight Changes and Cancellations:</b> Please refer to our booking policy for terms regarding
                    flight changes and cancellations.
                    Depending on your fare type, changes may be subject to fees.</li>
            </ul>
        </h6>

        <section id="visa-passport">
            <br><br>

            <h1 class="text-center m-4">Visa & Passport Requirements</h1>
            <img src="/assets/travel_info/visa1.jpg" alt="PassportImg"><br><br>
            <h5>
                <p>Before traveling internationally, ensure that you meet the following requirements:</p>
            </h5><br>

            <div class="cardSection">
                <div class="card mb-3" style="max-width: 540px;">
                    <div class="row g-0">
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                            <img src="/assets/travel_info/visa2.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded-start" alt="visaImg"
                                width="500" height="300">
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-8">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <h5 class="card-title">Visa Requirements</h5>
                                <p class="card-text">It is your responsibility to check and obtain the necessary visas
                                    for your destination country before departure.
                                    You may need a visa for:</p>
                                <ul>
                                    <li>Transit in a country</li>
                                    <li>Entry to your final destination</li>
                                    <li>Return or onward travel</li>
                                </ul>
                                <p class="card-text">We recommend you check with the embassy or consulate of the country
                                    you are
                                    visiting for the most current visa information.</p>
                                <p class="card-text"><small class="text-body-secondary">Last updated 1 year ago</small>
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
        </section>

        <div class="card mb-3" style="max-width: 540px;">
            <div class="row g-0">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <img src="/assets/travel_info/passport.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded-start" alt="PassportImg"
                        width="500" height="300">
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-8">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Passport Requirements</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">Ensure your passport is valid for at least six months beyond your planned
                            departure date.
                            If your passport is nearing expiration, renew it before traveling.
                            Some countries may require additional documentation (e.g., entry permits, health
                            certificates).</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li><b>For International Flights:</b> A valid passport is required for all international
                                travelers.</li>
                            <li><b>For Domestic Flights:</b> A government-issued ID may be sufficient, but please check
                                with your airline.</li>
                        </ul>

                        <p class="card-text"><small class="text-body-secondary">Last updated 1 year ago</small></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        </div><br>
        <h4>
            <p>We recommend arriving at the airport 3 hours before your international flight departure and 2 hours for
                domestic
                flights to allow sufficient time for passport control and security checks.</p>
        </h4>

        <div class="bottom">
            <div class="section pb-5">
                <h4>
                    For further questions or assistance, <br>feel free to contact our customer support team. <br>
                    <h1>Safe travels!</h1>
                </h4>
            </div>
        </div><br>



        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.11.8/dist/umd/popper.min.js"
            integrity="sha384-I7E8VVD/ismYTF4hNIPjVp/Zjvgyol6VFvRkX/vR+Vc4jQkC+hVqc2pM8ODewa9r"
            crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js"
            integrity="sha384-0pUGZvbkm6XF6gxjEnlmuGrJXVbNuzT9qBBavbLwCsOGabYfZo0T0to5eqruptLy"
            crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>

</html>